exts/workspace_governance/mod.rs`:\n```rust\npub const REQUIRED_WORKSPACE_DIRECTORIES: &[&str] =\n    &[\"projects\", \"requirements\", \"daemon/tasks\", \"daemon/leases\"];\n```\n\n---\n\n### 7. **Dependencies (Cargo.toml)**\n\n**Status: MINIMAL BUT SUITABLE**\n\nCurrent dependencies in `/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/Cargo.toml`:\n- tokio (multi-threaded async runtime)\n- serde/serde_json (JSON serialization)\n- clap (CLI parsing)\n- chrono (timestamps)\n- toml/toml_edit (config files)\n- thiserror (error handling)\n- tracing/tracing-subscriber (observability)\n\n**MISSING DEPENDENCIES FOR DAEMON:**\n- No git/gitoxide for worktree management\n- No gh CLI wrapper for GitHub integration\n- No tmux/pane management library\n- No task queue library (would need to build or choose one)\n- No process management (would use tokio + nix/std::process)\n\n---\n\n## Summary: What Exists vs What's Missing\n\n### EXISTS:\n- ✓ Workspace and project directory structure with daemon/tasks and daemon/leases placeholders\n- ✓ CLI command definitions for daemon (start, status, abort, retry, reconcile)\n- ✓ Domain model for contract labels (InvocationContract::Requirements { label })\n- ✓ Stage-to-role mapping for workflow stages\n- ✓ Run snapshot and journal persistence\n- ✓ Artifact/payload storage and querying\n- ✓ Requirements contract validation with domain-specific stages\n- ✓ FileSystem adapter for all project/run state operations\n- ✓ Stub backend adapter for testing\n\n### MISSING:\n- ✗ `automation_runtime` context implementation (empty shell only)\n- ✗ Task model and persistence (no task data structure, storage, or querying)\n- ✗ Lease model and reconciliation (no lease data structure or TTL logic)\n- ✗ Label parsing and routing logic (no parser, no router, no dispatcher)\n- ✗ Daemon task queue and dispatch mechanism\n- ✗ Git worktree adapter (no clone, checkout, create/remove worktree logic)\n- ✗ GitHub/issue integration adapter (no issue polling, no PR watcher, no gh CLI wrapper)\n- ✗ Process management for long-running daemon\n- ✗ Task lifecycle handlers (for each daemon subcommand)\n- ✗ Reconciliation engine\n- ✗ Conformance tests for daemon operations\n- ✗ Dependencies for git operations, process management, GitHub integration\n\n---\n\n## Relevant File Paths (Absolute)\n\n**Core Implementation:**\n- `/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/cli/daemon.rs` - Stubbed daemon CLI\n- `/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/automation_runtime/mod.rs` - Empty context\n- `/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/workspace_governance/mod.rs` - Workspace init with daemon dir structure\n\n**Domain Models:**\n- `/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/agent_execution/model.rs` - InvocationContract definition\n- `/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/project_run_record/model.rs` - Run/project models\n- `/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/requirements_drafting/model.rs` - Requirements contracts\n- `/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/shared/domain.rs` - Shared domain (FailureClass, BackendFamily, etc.)\n- `/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/shared/error.rs` - Error types\n\n**Tests & Specs:**\n- `/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/tests/conformance/features/workspace_init.feature` - Workspace structure expectations\n- `/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/Cargo.toml` - Dependencies\n\n**Reference Material:**\n- `/root/new-ralph-burning/rb.md` - Architecture spec describing daemon expectations\n- `/root/new-ralph-burning/multibackend-orchestration/src/daemon/` - Legacy implementation (read-only reference)"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a717b5cd2d072bc7b (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 53679\ntool_uses: 46\nduration_ms: 78268</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ac8d6a2a-5f6d-4606-9741-7014e6740f51","uuid":"95729